<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A new feature should be added.
It should be possible to use a sort of routing mechanism for non-translated messageid's.</p>

<p>If a messageid is not translated in a particular language it should automatically look for another defined language...
So you should be possible to do something like this:</p>

<p>Translate Spain:
String 1 not translated in spain -&gt; goto French -&gt; String 1 not translated in French -&gt; goto German -&gt; String 1 not translated in german  -&gt; return messageid</p>

<p>a new "setDefault" method should be able to define such fallback rules.
So strings which are not translatable in one language will be returned in another language.</p>

